 public void save(int inx,
                  int qnum,
                  int pcnt,
                  int type)
Store everything. Performs the functions of saveQNUM(int, int), savePCNT(int, int), saveTYPE(int, int, int)

qnum - the quadruple number to store
pcnt - which parameter
type - the type of the parameter
